  docs/RELEASING.md,project,"Canonical auto-release architecture,setup,changelog ownership,npm and Bun semantics,and recovery"
  README.md,project,Public release workflow overview
close_reason: "Implemented pm-cli-parity change-aware daily release preparation, lossless pm-changelog ownership, atomic release commit/tag creation, idempotent npm provenance publishing, exact npm/npx/Bun verification, scheduled blocker reporting, focused automation tests, and detailed maintainer documentation. Preservation proof retained all 19 legacy bullets and added seven previously omitted closed pm records; full release validation passed with 893 tests and zero failures."
body: ""
